data.title: Judy Garland Museum - Grand Rapids - Tickets
data.meta_description: Experience the Judy Garland Museum in Grand Rapids, Minnesota! Explore the Wizard of Oz collection, birthplace home, and interactive Children's Discovery Museum. Get your tickets!
data.text:
⭐ Judy Garland Museum should be experienced because it offers a unique destination with a large Judy Garland and Wizard of Oz collection, a restored birthplace home, a Judy Garland Gallery, an interactive Children's Discovery Museum, and exhibits and artifacts for all generations.

Tickets for Judy Garland Museum

🎫 Adult (13+)

🎫 Child (1-12)

Judy Garland Museum and Discovery Museum options available

Highlights

🏰 Residence of an abundant compilation of Judy Garland and Wizard of Oz memorabilia

🏡 Revived 1920's birth home of Judy Garland

🎪 Engaging museum specifically designed for children's exploration

General Info

📍 Location: Judy Garland Museum

📅 Dates and times: select your dates/times directly in the ticket selector

👤 Age requirement: all ages are welcome

♿ Accessibility: this experience is wheelchair accessible

❓ For this event, all sales are final and tickets can’t be refunded, changed or modified. For more information, please refer to our T&Cs
